p.seg:
Elles disent : le
                       Louvre, la place Royale, mais elles usent de tours et de phrases plutôt
                    que de prononcer de certains noms ;

or if by chance
                       they let such a word slip, 
                    they will excuse it as if it were criminal;

he fits four hours together at
                    Aracia's, where he ventures his 5 or 6 
                    pistoles e'ry night;
